+    /// | Full             | Full      |
+    /// | SimpleBorders    | Reduced   |
+    /// | NoStyling        | Reduced   |
+    /// | EssentialOnly    | Off       |
+    /// | Skeleton         | Off       |
+    /// | SkipFrame        | Off       |
